Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:13.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:27.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请原谅我当时无礼的冒犯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会变成这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.75,0:00:40.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要当心别伤到她了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么要上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.57,0:00:48.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然如我所料
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:52.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你作为一名士兵也根本不够格
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:56.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别以为我会就这样认输！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:00:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太天真了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.74,0:01:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天真的是你吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.38,0:01:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.46,0:01:20.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安格尔波达的女神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.97,0:01:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请保佑父亲大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.76,0:01:25.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请为狼族带来胜利
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//--------------------OPJP--------------------
